arStrings.szText: My apologies for the runaround. With how boisterous Backwater’s been lately, we’re drawing some unwanted attention to our humble town.
You see, officially, it’s not on any maps. To keep it that way, I’ve set up a deal my more bloodthirsty brethren might not want to approach so diplomatically.
I have the supplies stashed nearby. We find it, pay off the law men, and you get an easy payday.
